oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Mel Tillis and Buddy Rick at the Waynesboro Senior High School Auditorium on October 23. Poster features metal photoplates of Mel Tillis and Buddy Rick. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see http://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/cdm/ref/collection/hatch3/id/28240.
